title: Hermes Cabasellier 31 Tote
description: Hermes Cabasellier 31 tote bag in ivory Taurillon Clemence leather (U: 2022). Featuring dual flat handles, white stitches, a hanging flat pocket at front. The open top reveals to tonal suede spacious interior. Approximate dimensions: 31cm(W) x 25cm(H) x 10cm(D), 25cm handle drop. Accompanied by Hermes dust bag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
